{"tid":945032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幣少爺 ] 黄鉦傑，原名關梓傑，是位更新人士，靠實力闖出一片天。。","createTime":"2018-12-17T14:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T05:14:41.000Z","uid":103156,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a256a09ed61168d5a657b86589f7ef04d90f5ade","tid":945032,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"【22:08更新】消息稱，「幣少爺」黃鉦傑原名關梓傑，他在2012年曾任游泳教練，當時他因在九龍公園泳池盜竊手機罪成，被法官判處160小時社會服務令，其後他改名為黃鉦傑。<br />\n<br />\n【天降銀紙】警方把「幣少爺」押返荃灣公司蒐證 重案組接手<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59038010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59038010&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0159621f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59038010&h=e3e0dba0\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59038010</a>"},{"pid":"23b8b859c3b40e82d587e711e4f081c86fd463ed","tid":945032,"uid":103156,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"網名「幣少爺」的黃鉦傑昨日在深水埔派錢期間被警方拘捕後，其背景被越揭越多。原名關梓傑的「幣少爺」現年24歲，原居公屋，草根出身，就讀天主教南華中學，畢業後曾在快餐店和地盤工作。《星島日報》今年7月底向他求證，對方承認關梓傑是其本人。而今日有消息爆出，「幣少爺」19歲時曾當游泳教練。<br />\n<br />\n「幣少爺」曾在推介Filecoin的講座中分享個人投資比特幣的成功經歷。當時稱，省吃儉用下，於2015年以數十萬港元買入比特幣，於去年比特幣價格介乎1.4萬至1.5萬美元全數沽出，共「賺了八位數字」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1389843/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1389843%2F&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=611fba0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1389843%2F&h=94b9d37b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1389843/</a>"},{"pid":"8cd2fcaedb1c00c593a31015b39b1c1565b88bcc","tid":945032,"uid":49392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"廿歲省吃儉用儲到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc167d2f17319000af2d1c386d8d6d56e091e73","tid":945032,"uid":59511,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"12年窮到要偷手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n15年就自稱慳到幾十萬買bitcoin<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce16856f73f5e1c509350c62332b8bc53b83230","tid":945032,"uid":92278,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"我信第一段係真"},{"pid":"a945e800d728e8555316ba02b7e60efb8f7d13e4","tid":945032,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"教游水年幾兩年就儲到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f1b2a4694c312a62ebb9e5e9585d8636e6eb8f","tid":945032,"uid":44454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a945e800d728e8555316ba02b7e60efb8f7d13e4","tid":945032,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"教游水年幾兩年就儲到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"應該偷左好多部手機"},{"pid":"a3df693a7f67e5cf05dc3dad3073a6fbc855ab66","tid":945032,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8cd2fcaedb1c00c593a31015b39b1c1565b88bcc","tid":945032,"uid":49392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"廿歲省吃儉用儲到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"唔通老實話又偷又呃得返來咩"},{"pid":"ea0ecb9b2416329e64e7a226fe860cbb782fb710","tid":945032,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"【天降銀紙】幣少爺曾是公屋仔 與大賭李嘉誠影畢業照<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59041020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59041020&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f8580dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59041020&h=c5f8273a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59041020</a><br />\n<br />\n原來，<span style=\"color: red;\">幣少爺過往也是一名「公屋仔」，與4年前賣「山埃賭波貼士」的「大賭李嘉誠」陳冠霖份屬好友</span>，忽然富貴的行徑，也不過是在過去一年才顯露。網上流傳了二人的畢業合照。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳黃鉦傑發迹的蛛絲馬跡，有討論區指<span style=\"color: red;\">他曾自稱「幕sir」，開游泳班招攬學員，卻在錢銀到手後消聲匿迹 </span>。據黃鉦傑自稱，他投身職場時先後在地盤和麥當勞打工，儲蓄了數十萬元並用來炒Bitcoin，然後變出8位數字的身家。<br />\n<br />\n踏入2018年後，他忽然拋出一個大計，四處向人宣傳若要食正新一代虛擬貨幣「filecoin」浪潮，就要向他買filecoin礦機，加入他的「幣少軍團」。按黃鉦傑在facebook最後公開的價單，一部礦機索價27,500元，他聲稱「幣少軍團」約300人，又在另一個微信群組吸納了3,000人加入。在這場大茶飯中，黃鉦傑吸金額難以估量。"},{"pid":"06ab2825cad6a81405910cba166520fe7299f7ae","tid":945032,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XpznQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XpznQE.jpg&h=47f0bd97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收嘢呀！"},{"pid":"641c193060744d2e6626cca67cf9ad43c9a5c6da","tid":945032,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxZ3Zb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjxZ3Zb4.png&h=2cde3bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幣少軍一句解釋晒所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma