17T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"【天降銀紙】幣少爺曾是公屋仔 與大賭李嘉誠影畢業照<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59041020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59041020&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f8580dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59041020&h=c5f8273a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59041020</a><br />\n<br />\n原來，<span style=\"color: red;\">幣少爺過往也是一名「公屋仔」，與4年前賣「山埃賭波貼士」的「大賭李嘉誠」陳冠霖份屬好友</span>，忽然富貴的行徑，也不過是在過去一年才顯露。網上流傳了二人的畢業合照。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳黃鉦傑發迹的蛛絲馬跡，有討論區指<span style=\"color: red;\">他曾自稱「幕sir」，開游泳班招攬學員，卻在錢銀到手後消聲匿迹 </span>。據黃鉦傑自稱，他投身職場時先後在地盤和麥當勞打工，儲蓄了數十萬元並用來炒Bitcoin，然後變出8位數字的身家。<br />\n<br />\n踏入2018年後，他忽然拋出一個大計，四處向人宣傳若要食正新一代虛擬貨幣「filecoin」浪潮，就要向他買filecoin礦機，加入他的「幣少軍團」。按黃鉦傑在facebook最後公開的價單，一部礦機索價27,500元，他聲稱「幣少軍團」約300人，又在另一個微信群組吸納了3,000人加入。在這場大茶飯中，黃鉦傑吸金額難以估量。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"兩個都正仆街"},{"pid":"f8e33d040c9b349072fc508460e06fe7338e9b62","tid":945032,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T22:16:29.000Z","msg":"幾時到火撩陰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103c23dccacfe09ec680d642155b4d98c660c831","tid":945032,"uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46e90056557e6f457781786a2f9da4d02a7174a7","tid":945032,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ea0ecb9b2416329e64e7a226fe860cbb782fb710","tid":945032,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"【天降銀紙】幣少爺曾是公屋仔 與大賭李嘉誠影畢業照<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181217&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59041020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181217%26s%